column1: #Text=Is Sweden really so bad as some want us to believe?
#Text=I apologise for not speaking Swedish, but I am a bit curious about other countries and espeically of their political system and culture.
#Text=I am college student from Croatia and need to make a seminar on Sweden.
#Text=So, there is not many English based sources on swedish political culture, with the exception of "The New Totalitarians" of Roland Huntford.
#Text=The news article are often also sound very unrealistic and bizzare.
#Text=So one of the recent news is that Swedish PM want to make a law in which a written contract is needed to have sexual intercourse (.
#Text=claims a man was prosecuted for eating bacon.
#Text=I personally have hard to believe all of this, so how true is it?.
